uccess, not viral videos.","keyPoints":["Prva komercijalna inačica Atlasa u Hyundaijevoj tvornici","Snaga i preciznost s ograničenjima: baterija, održavanje, okolina","Demo vs. deployment: razlika između koreografije i skladišnog poda"],"source":{"name":"","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sd8ivhpjI6g"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/atlas-steps-out-of-the-labinto-hyundais-factory-fl/main.jpg","alt":"Atlas odlazi u tvornicu – a demo završava"},"subtitle":"Od laboratorijskih uvjeta do industrijske prakse: jaz koji ostaje između YouTube snimaka i stvarnog radnog dana","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/atlas-steps-out-of-the-labinto-hyundais-factory-fl/subtitle.png","alt":"Od laboratorijskih uvjeta do industrijske prakse: jaz koji ostaje između YouTube snimaka i stvarnog radnog dana"},"tags":["Boston Dynamics","Humanoid Robotics","Industrial Automation"],"geo":{"name":"Ulsan, South Korea","lat":35.5384,"lon":129.3114,"countryCode":"KR"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$7","videoUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sd8ivhpjI6g","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-demining-drones-show-promise-but-battery-life-is-a","title":"Dronovi i AI protiv mina: radi li to izvan laba?","category":"robotics","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Godinu dana nakon što je 1.","execSummary":"The article dissects the gap between AI/drone demining demos and real-world deployment, focusing on hardware limits (battery, sensors, weather resilience), certification hurdles, and the persistent reliance on human verification. It challenges the narrative of 'revolutionary' tech by asking who actually benefits when prototypes fail in mud, rain, or dense vegetation—conditions where most mines actually exist.","keyPoints":["1.945 mrtvih, 4.325 ozlijeđenih – polovina djece","AI prepoznaje mine, ali tlo i vlaga remete senzore","Certifikacija i troškovi: što koči masovno korištenje"],"source":{"name":"TechXplore Robotics","url":"https://techxplore.com/news/2026-03-combining-drones-ai-faster-safer.html"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/demining-drones-show-promise-but-battery-life-is-a/main.jpg","alt":"Dronovi i AI protiv mina: radi li to izvan laba?"},"subtitle":"Od demo videa do prave deminacije: koliko je to stvarno skalabilno?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/demining-drones-show-promise-but-battery-life-is-a/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Od demo videa do prave deminacije: koliko je to stvarno skalabilno?"},"tags":["Mine Clearance","Drone Technology","Autonomous Demining","Explosive Ordnance Disposal"],"geo":{"name":"Bosna i Hercegovina","lat":43.9159,"lon":17.6791,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$8","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-bristol-s-motor-networks-mimic-musclebut-can-they-","title":"Mišićna mreža koja oponaša ljudsku snagu – radi li to i izvan laba?","category":"robotics","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada znanstvenici s Univerziteta u Bristolu kažu da su razvili mrežu mehaničkih motora koja oponaša ljudske mišiće na molekularnoj razini, prva reakcija je – naravno – skepticizam.","execSummary":"Bristol researchers built a mechanical motor network mimicking human muscle behavior under load—impressive in theory, but real-world deployment faces hardware limits, scalability costs, and environmental durability gaps. The article dissects the divide between lab demos and industrial readiness, targeting engineers who need to separate hype from viable tech.","keyPoints":["Mehanički motori kopiraju molekularnu mašineriju ljudskih mišića","Potencijal za umjetne mišiće u robotici – ali gdje su granice?","Od laboratorija do skladišta: koliko je ovo spremno za stvarni svijet?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/bristol-s-motor-networks-mimic-musclebut-can-they-/main.jpg","alt":"Mišićna mreža koja oponaša ljudsku snagu – radi li to i izvan laba?"},"subtitle":"Demo izgleda obećavajuće, ali može li preživjeti mokri utorak u industriji?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/bristol-s-motor-networks-mimic-musclebut-can-they-/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Demo izgleda obećavajuće, ali može li preživjeti mokri utorak u industriji?"},"tags":["Muscle Network","Humanoid Robotics","Industrial Automation"],"geo":{"name":"Bristol, United Kingdom","lat":51.454514,"lon":-2.58791,"countryCode":"GB"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$9","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-solar-farm-robots-can-they-survive-outside-the-dem","title":"Robot gradi solarne farme 24/7: Terafab V2 spreman za tržište","category":"robotics","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"SAD treba više električne energije, i to brzo — a Terabase Energy iz Berkeleyja vjeruje da roboti mogu premostiti jaz između ambicija i stvarne izgradnje.","execSummary":"Terabase Energy's Terafab V2 solar construction robot has completed field testing and is now commercially available, marking a potential shift from demo-controlled robotics to real-world deployment. The system's ability to operate autonomously in uncontrolled environments will determine whether this represents genuine industrial automation progress.","keyPoints":["Terafab V2 završio terensko testiranje","Autonomni sustav koristi AI za gradnju","Rješenje za nedostatak radne snage"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/solar-farm-robots-can-they-survive-outside-the-dem/main.jpg","alt":"Robot gradi solarne farme 24/7: Terafab V2 spreman za tržište"},"subtitle":"Od kontroliranog testa do prašnjavog gradilišta","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/solar-farm-robots-can-they-survive-outside-the-dem/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Od kontroliranog testa do prašnjavog gradilišta"},"tags":["Terafab V2","Solar Farm Maintenance","Industrial Automation"],"geo":{"name":"San Francisco, US","lat":37.7749,"lon":-122.4194,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$a","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-ukraines-drones-can-they-outfly-dji-without-chinas","title":"Ukrajinski dronovi protiv DJI: Što Pentagon zapravo kupuje?","category":"robotics","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada Pentagon [potpiše ugovore](https://www.","execSummary":"The US Army's billion-dollar bet on Ukrainian drones isn't just about avoiding Chinese components—it's a high-stakes test of whether non-Chinese hardware can meet real-world military demands. The Shrike 10 Fiber and F10 models impress on paper, but their deployment readiness hinges on unproven scalability, maintenance logistics, and durability in harsh environments, exposing the gap between procurement decisions and operational reality.","keyPoints":["Pentagon izbjegava kineske komponente — ukrajinski dronovi dobivaju ugovore","Shrike 10 Fiber i F10: što mogu van demonstracije?","Masovna proizvodnja zahtijeva više od „ne-kineske“ etikete"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/ukraines-drones-can-they-outfly-dji-without-chinas/main.jpg","alt":"Ukrajinski dronovi protiv DJI: Što Pentagon zapravo kupuje?"},"subtitle":"Od labsa do prakse: Koliko su ukrajinski dronovi spremni za stvarne misije?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/ukraines-drones-can-they-outfly-dji-without-chinas/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Od labsa do prakse: Koliko su ukrajinski dronovi spremni za stvarne misije?"},"tags":["Ukrainian Drones","DJI","Military Drone Deployment"],"geo":{"name":"San Francisco, US","lat":37.7749,"lon":-122.4194,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$b","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-20-accidental-hacker-gets-30k-for-7-000-robot-securit","title":"DJI plaća 30K za slučajni haking 7000 robovaca","category":"robotics","date":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Valentinovo 2024.","execSummary":"A seemingly harmless PlayStation hack exposed 7,000 DJI robovacs to potential privacy breaches, revealing critical IoT scaling flaws. The incident highlights how demo-ready products often lack deployment-grade security, especially in cloud architecture—raising questions about DJI’s prioritization of speed over safety in mass-market robotics.","keyPoints":["PlayStation kontroler otkrio ranjivost u DJI-jevim robovacima","7000 uređaja izloženo potencijalnom pristupu privatnim prostorima","Bug bounty program ili pokriveni sigurnosni propust?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/accidental-hacker-gets-30k-for-7-000-robot-securit/main.jpg","alt":"DJI plaća 30K za slučajni haking 7000 robovaca"},"subtitle":"Kada hobi postane sigurnosni incident: što nam ovo govori o IoT skaliranju","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/accidental-hacker-gets-30k-for-7-000-robot-securit/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kada hobi postane sigurnosni incident: što nam ovo govori o IoT skaliranju"},"tags":["DJI","Drone Hacking","IoT Security"],"geo":{"name":"Shenzhen, China","lat":22.5431,"lon":114.0579,"countryCode":"CN"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$c","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-20-electronic-dolphin-a-robot-that-fits-in-your-shoeb","title":"Elektronički delfin: robot veličine patike za čišćenje naftnih mrlja","category":"robotics","date":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada se dogodi naftni proliv, svaka minuta je presudna – ali čišćenje je i dalje sporo, skupo i često neefikasno.","execSummary":"RMIT’s sneaker-sized ‘Electronic Dolphin’ robot uses a sea-urchin-inspired filter to clean oil spills, but its real-world applicability is constrained by battery life, scalability, and controlled-testing limitations. The article dissects the gap between demo capabilities and deployment readiness, focusing on niche use cases (ports, coastal areas) while questioning hardware durability and operational costs—critical for an industry where seconds and reliability matter more than innovation hype.","keyPoints":["Robot inspiriran morskim ježevima filtrira naftu u realnom vremenu","Daleko od masovne upotrebe: ograničenja baterije i skalabilnosti","Zašto bi ova tehnologija mogla biti korisna u lukama, a ne na otvorenom moru"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/electronic-dolphin-a-robot-that-fits-in-your-shoeb/main.jpg","alt":"Elektronički delfin: robot veličine patike za čišćenje naftnih mrlja"},"subtitle":"Od labsa do prakse: koliko je ovaj ‘delfin’ spreman za prljave poslove?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/electronic-dolphin-a-robot-that-fits-in-your-shoeb/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Od labsa do prakse: koliko je ovaj ‘delfin’ spreman za prljave poslove?"},"tags":["Oil Spill Cleanup","Marine Robotics","Autonomous Underwater Vehicle"],"geo":{"name":"Melbourne, Australia","lat":-37.8136,"lon":144.9631,"countryCode":"AU"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$d","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-20-faa-greenlights-real-world-air-taxi-testing-across","title":"FAA otvara nebo za air taxi: radi li to stvarno?","category":"robotics","date":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Američka Federalna uprava za zrakoplovstvo (FAA) konačno je otvorila vrata za realne testove zračnih taksija – ili, preciznije, za osam pilota programa rasprostrtimh po 26 američkih država.","execSummary":"The FAA’s approval of eight eVTOL pilot programs marks a shift from controlled demos to real-world testing—but the gap between a polished video and scalable deployment remains vast. This analysis cuts through the hype to examine hardware limits (battery life, payload, autonomy), regulatory hurdles, and the few use cases (like medical cargo) where the tech might actually deliver near-term value.","keyPoints":["Osam pilota u 26 država – prvi pravi testovi eVTOL-ova","Urbani taksi, hitna medicina, autonomni let: tko to zapravo treba?","Baterije, certifikacija i „mokri utorak“ – gdje će stati?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/faa-greenlights-real-world-air-taxi-testing-across/main.jpg","alt":"FAA otvara nebo za air taxi: radi li to stvarno?"},"subtitle":"Od odobrenih programa do stvarnog letenja: koliko je to od demo-a do deploymenta?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/faa-greenlights-real-world-air-taxi-testing-across/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Od odobrenih programa do stvarnog letenja: koliko je to od demo-a do deploymenta?"},"tags":["Air Taxi","FAA","Urban Air Mobility","Deployment","Regulation"],"geo":{"name":"United States, US","lat":39.8283,"lon":-98.5795,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$e","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-16-4d-vision-on-a-chip-what-the-demo-doesn-t-show","title":"4D vizija za robote: radi li to stvarno ili je samo demo?","category":"robotics","date":"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Istraživači su uspjeli integrirati preko pola milijuna mikroskopskih komponenti na jedan silicijski čip, stvarajući napredni kamerijski sustav koji istodobno bilježi trodimenzionalno okruženje i brzinu pokretnih objekata.","execSummary":"A new compact imaging sensor promises 4D vision for robots by combining 3D mapping with velocity measurement, but its real-world applicability remains uncertain. The article explores the gap between lab demonstrations and practical deployment, analyzing hardware limitations, scalability challenges, and potential industrial use cases.","source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/4d-vision-on-a-chip-what-the-demo-doesn-t-show/main.jpg","alt":"4D vizija za robote: radi li to stvarno ili je samo demo?"},"subtitle":"Od labsa do prakse: što ovaj kompaktni senzor zaista može?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/4d-vision-on-a-chip-what-the-demo-doesn-t-show/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Od labsa do prakse: što ovaj kompaktni senzor zaista može?"},"tags":["4D Vision","Robotic Perception","Computer Vision","Silicon Chip","Autonomy"],"geo":{"name":"Global","lat":0,"lon":0,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$f","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-10-ais-new-control-knob-less-data-more-precisionif-yo","title":"Periodni sustav za AI: Što to znači za multimodalne modele?","category":"robotics","date":"2026-03-10T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-10T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Izbor pravog pristupa za **multimodalne AI modele** – oni koji kombiniraju tekst, slike, zvuk i druge podatke – dosad je bio pitanje probanja i pogrešaka.","source":{"name":"Future Pulse","url":"https://futurepulse.hr"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/ais-new-control-knob-less-data-more-precisionif-yo/main.jpg","alt":"Periodni sustav za AI: Što to znači za multimodalne modele?"},"subtitle":"Novi matematički okvir može smanjiti troškove i povećati točnost – ali će ga industrija prihvatiti?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/ais-new-control-knob-less-data-more-precisionif-yo/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Novi matematički okvir može smanjiti troškove i povećati točnost – ali će ga industrija prihvatiti?"},"tags":["future-pulse","automated","robotics"],"geo":{"name":"Atlanta, United States","lat":33.749,"lon":-84.388,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$10","lang":"hr"}],"basePath":"/hr"}]]}],["$L11"],"$L12"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
